      "source": [
        "import cv2\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "\n",
        "net = cv2.dnn.readNet(\"/content/yolov3.weights\", \"/content/yolov3.cfg\")\n",
        "layer_names = net.getLayerNames()\n",
        "output_layers = [layer_names[i - 1] for i in net.getUnconnectedOutLayers()]\n",
        "\n",
        "# Load COCO classes\n",
        "# Assuming coco.names is also in the content directory\n",
        "with open(\"/content/coco.names\", \"r\") as f:\n",
        "    classes = f.read().strip().split(\"\\n\")\n",
        "\n",
        "# Load image\n",
        "image_path = \"/content/testingpic.jpeg\"  # Change this to your image path\n",
        "image = cv2.imread(image_path)\n",
        "height, width = image.shape[:2]\n",
        "\n",
        "# Preprocess image for YOLO\n",
        "blob = cv2.dnn.blobFromImage(image, 0.00392, (416, 416), swapRB=True, crop=False)\n",
        "net.setInput(blob)\n",
        "outs = net.forward(output_layers)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Extract detections\n",
        "class_ids, confidences, boxes = [], [], []\n",
        "for out in outs:\n",
        "    for detection in out:\n",
        "        scores = detection[5:]\n",
        "        class_id = np.argmax(scores)\n",
        "        confidence = scores[class_id]\n",
        "        if confidence > 0.5:  # Confidence threshold\n",
        "            center_x, center_y, w, h = (detection[:4] * [width, height, width, height]).astype(\"int\")\n",
        "            x, y = int(center_x - w / 2), int(center_y - h / 2)\n",
        "            boxes.append([x, y, w, h])\n",
        "            confidences.append(float(confidence))\n",
        "            class_ids.append(class_id)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Apply Non-Maximum Suppression (NMS)\n",
        "indices = cv2.dnn.NMSBoxes(boxes, confidences, 0.5, 0.4)\n",
        "for i in indices.flatten():\n",
        "    x, y, w, h = boxes[i]\n",
        "    label = f\"{classes[class_ids[i]]}: {confidences[i]:.2f}\"\n",
        "    cv2.rectangle(image, (x, y), (x + w, y + h), (0, 255, 0), 2)\n",
        "    cv2.putText(image, label, (x, y - 10), cv2.FONT_HERSHEY_SIMPLEX, 0.5, (0, 255, 0), 2)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Show output image (Replace cv2.imshow)\n",
        "from google.colab.patches import cv2_imshow\n",
        "\n",
        "cv2_imshow(image)  # Use cv2_imshow instead of cv2.imshow()\n",
        "cv2.waitKey(0)\n",
        "cv2.destroyAllWindows()\n"
      ],

        "import torch\n",
        "import cv2\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "from utils.general import non_max_suppression, scale_coords\n",
        "from utils.plots import plot_one_box\n",
        "from models.experimental import attempt_load\n",
        "\n",
        "# Load YOLOv7 model\n",
        "device = torch.device(\"cuda\" if torch.cuda.is_available() else \"cpu\")\n",
        "model = attempt_load(\"yolov7.pt\", map_location=device)  # Load YOLOv7 weights\n",
        "model.eval()\n",
        "\n",
        "# Load image\n",
        "image_path = \"/content/testingpic.jpeg\"  # Change this to your image path\n",
        "image = cv2.imread(image_path)\n",
        "h, w = image.shape[:2]\n",
        "\n",
        "# Convert image for YOLOv7\n",
        "img = cv2.cvtColor(image, cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB)\n",
        "img = cv2.resize(img, (640, 640))  # Resize to YOLOv7 input size\n",
        "img = img.astype(np.float32) / 255.0  # Normalize\n",
        "img = torch.from_numpy(img).permute(2, 0, 1).unsqueeze(0).to(device)  # Convert to tensor\n",
        "\n",
        "# Perform inference\n",
        "with torch.no_grad():\n",
        "    pred = model(img)[0]\n",
        "\n",
        "# Apply Non-Maximum Suppression (NMS)\n",
        "pred = non_max_suppression(pred, 0.5, 0.45)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Process detections\n",
        "for det in pred:\n",
        "    if len(det):\n",
        "        det[:, :4] = scale_coords(img.shape[2:], det[:, :4], image.shape).round()\n",
        "        for *xyxy, conf, cls in det:\n",
        "            label = f\"{conf:.2f}\"\n",
        "            plot_one_box(xyxy, image, label=label, color=(0, 255, 0), line_thickness=2)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Show output image\n",
        "from google.colab.patches import cv2_imshow\n",
        "\n",
        "cv2_imshow(image)  # Use cv2_imshow for Google Colab\n",
        "cv2.waitKey(0)\n",
        "cv2.destroyAllWindows()\n"
      ],
